title: Greedy Viking2.0.1.apk
description:
ABSOLUTLY FREEEEEEEEEEEEEE!!!!!!!!
Description
Play the most addictive game of the decade.
Test how Greedy you are with Greedy Viking. How far you will go to risk your life for the beautiful sparkling Diamonds. Show your skill in collecting diamonds.The better your Hand Eye coordination, the more the diamonds. Use your Sharp brain to analyse the coming situation and act quickly. Understand the Physics of the 3 world Grass,Ice,Rubber and act accordingly.
Make High Scores and Share your Scores with your Friends with Google+.
Play Greedy Viking and end your Boring Days.
